{"tid":472432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又埋單］39歲「小飛俠」林燕玲嫁金融才俊","createTime":"2017-11-18T08:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T05:16:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"f56904b2cf58a17885b3bcb7c0ec2f9aa07ac8f7","tid":472432,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/163228_c6dd680a5346774011f6b25dc59031db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F163228_c6dd680a5346774011f6b25dc59031db.jpg&h=e40ec4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/163322_f2a1e3790176672523ec69d415f2612b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F163322_f2a1e3790176672523ec69d415f2612b.jpg&h=5ad55798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恭喜恭喜！現職公關公司嘅前無綫主播「小飛俠」林燕玲（Ruby），同任職基金管理公司嘅男友葉浩文（Kirk），宣佈結婚喇！<br />\n<br />\n今午兩人分別於fb貼婚紗相，寫道：「We are married! The new chapter of our life story starts from today。我們結婚了！從今天起將展開我們人生的新一頁。謝謝大家祝福！」恭喜恭喜！<br />\n<br />\n人稱「小飛俠」嘅林燕玲，今年39歲，大學時主修生物化學，畢業後先後效力無綫新聞台主播及Now財經主播，及後轉戰銀行界，現為麗新集團傳訊部副總裁，即係，幫林建岳打工。<br />\n<br />\n；Kirk葉浩文由澳洲及美國回流香港，現職基金高級副總裁，不時於財經電台、電視節目及開辦講座，練得一身結實肌肉，年近40，簡單嚟講就係「金融才俊」啦。果然係襯絕。<br />\n<br />\n前主播駱文捷負責做司儀，佢以短訊恭賀一對新人﹕「恭喜他們白頭到老，永結同心！」<br />\n而林燕玲未有接聽電話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171118/57474359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171118%2F57474359&d=yAza6%2BG8uP2PGvR%2Bc5vk3jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=69537dde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171118%2F57474359&h=7310920d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171118/57474359</a>"},{"pid":"0235c5c0e85a81a560ff5bf982a1edd2b84bbc06","tid":472432,"uid":29804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:43:19.000Z","msg":"終於有人要"},{"pid":"1229b1408b4160fe6e1958455fa421acbe5ab5fd","tid":472432,"uid":56328,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"39仲有冇得生，金融才俊都要埋老單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4236cb4b5dd6a520d408df4392de79bf81f8db7d","tid":472432,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>39仲有冇得生，金融才俊都要埋老單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嫖老殘妓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0031aefaa8ae4079acc3a42b18f4ccd52d6828dc","tid":472432,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:45:47.000Z","msg":"睇錯林志玲"},{"pid":"8e0112fa2cd9c2f0ceb17525bf4d4ce900500661","tid":472432,"uid":8515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"C.馬超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc75ad48cb23990e43f7531cbb86eabc72596373","tid":472432,"uid":22858,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAA